Uses of Class
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.bridge.JsoBuilder

Packages that use JsoBuilder
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client Defines the Rhizosphere visualization widget and all the main interfaces required to configure and instantiate a Rhizosphere visualization within GWT. 
com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.bridge Defines functionality to map bi-directionally between custom POJOs used as representation of Rhizosphere models and equivalent custom-tailored JavaScriptObjects that the underlying Rhizosphere javascript library can understand.
